A robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth for attention, while camera crews from the university media team capture interviews during the event. Career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops as students line up outside the gym before the fair opens, with announcement chimes signaling the time remaining as the fair enters its final hour and interview sign-up sheets being filled. Alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station. At the end of the event, a post-event survey link flashes on monitors near the exit, while volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures.

As the final hour of the fair approaches, announcement chimes signal the time remaining for participants to engage in the events.
